Default Arguments 

    we can passs default arguments to a function in its function prototype 
    say we have a function repcahar,
    void repchar( char = '*',int = 45); //prototype
    now you may even call the function withour arguments 
    it works, even you can do something like this too 
    repchar('='); //only default char variable is overiden here

Variable storage scope 
    
    Automatic Variable      Local       //lifetime till function ends
    Static Variable         Global      //lifetime till the program ends 


Object and Classes
    
    Data Handling - Private public 
    // Hiding data from developers not allowing them to commit honest mistakes
    Data Members 
    // The data inside the class 
    Member functions
    // The functions inside a class 
    Constructor
    // Function to automatically initilize stuff inside of a class
    
